	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Hi,
<br />I'm coding a 6502 dissasembler and now i have a problem. 
<br />How identify if a byte is an Opcode or a piece of Data (like texts New Game, Press Start, etc..) ?
<br />
<br />thxs...

		

		</td>
	</tr>
